{"tid":1786151,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際戰線] 除咗twitter，仲有一到需要打","createTime":"2019-12-17T02:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T07:20:51.000Z","uid":113784,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7351b6ee541bb9162d08301f721ddec0e4abcd","tid":1786151,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T02:39:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就係Quora</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nQuora係一個國際平台，俾世界各地嘅人問問題，再由熟悉嗰個領域嘅人回答<br />\n有啲似Yahoo知識咁<br />\n<br />\n我有follow Hong Kong呢個topic<br />\n唔睇都唔知，入面答問題嘅人近乎所有都極藍<br />\n會稱呼示威者為&rsquo;rioters&rsquo; 又盛<br />\nincluding but not limited to:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s1eHefm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1eHefm.png&h=ebe17f30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2Sd5m2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2Sd5m2.png&h=44c9be6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gwywR13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgwywR13.png&h=e7a7c99c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再係咁落去 香港俾外界嘅形象會節節下跌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>好希望英文唔錯嘅朋友幫手打下呢條戰線</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcf22a6f926d2e9f9c7544476b1370069d831f8","tid":1786151,"uid":319687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"我見quora 每個post 關於香港最多不高於2千人"},{"pid":"2bac8e90224b6011be71813dfd72836dae1479f5","tid":1786151,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dcf22a6f926d2e9f9c7544476b1370069d831f8","tid":1786151,"uid":319687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"我見quora 每個post 關於香港最多不高於2千人"},"citedBy":1,"